157 §36-21-224
158 (a) Approval for the scholarship shall be granted to an
159 eligible dependent upon submission of the documentation
160 required under Section 36-11-223 and shall continue for each
161 academic period for which the scholarship may be available as
162 provided in Section 36-11-222(a) on the following conditions:
163 (1) That the recipient complies with the Standards of
164 Satisfactory Academic Progress (SAP) as required for Title IV
165 benefits under the federal Higher Education Act and as defined
166 by the participating institution for each academic period for
167 which the recipient is enrolled.
168 (2) That the recipient maintain his or her full-time
